        <p>Patterns of microhomology (red), non-templated sequence (teal) or direct end-joining (yellow) in the chromothripsis rearrangements for each sample. The x axis shows the number of bases of microhomology (right of 0) or non-templated sequence (left of 0) for each rearrangement. The y axis shows the number of rearrangements in the sample showing that pattern of microhomology or non-templated sequence.</p>
